      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTABLACK TIGER (10) had a win at this track two runs ago before finishing second at his latest appearance over 2200m at this track, beaten 9 metres. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point. This is a nice drop in grade so he is in the right race to return to the winners' list. INTRUSION (9) finished seventh last start over 1720m at Melton, beaten 21 metres, after filling a minor placing at the previous appearance over 2300m at Menangle. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. Has the ability to find the winners' list. SABINE (5) was in the money two starts ago then things went amiss last start when she broke and finished 11 metres away in fourth over 2200m at this track. Beautifully placed and is able to make amends. THE SHALLOWS (3) is worth some thought after his last-start fifth over 2200m at this track on June 21.",
